file_content.text: [The remainder of the Eradicator command codes is stored in this terminal. Inputting your half will grant full control over the devices.]
[The ship's computer has sent a targeting sequence to the Eradicators. Jadus's attack on the Empire has begun.]
[The Eradicators have been placed on standby, and their rampage has been halted. They will not fire unless they receive new commands.]
